Package: rptPlus
Type: Package
Title: R Package Template - advanced
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Boris Steipe
Maintainer: Boris Steipe <boris.steipe@utoronto.ca>
Description: rpt contains an easy to adapt set of files for R package
             development, loosely based on Hadley Wickham's
             R-packages book. This advanced version includes files to create
             a Shiny package alongside with the package.
